        <title>hugo&#43;obsidian搭建个人博客记录1️⃣</title>
        <link>https://blog.dededuud.cn/p/hugo-obsidian%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%951%EF%B8%8F%E2%83%A3/</link>
